title: Apartment for rent: Levantplein 8, Amsterdam
description:
Lovely 3-room apartment of approximately 73m2 on the KNSM island!

- Good accessibility, with quick access to the A-10 ring road via the Piet Heijntunnel
- Close to shopping center Brazilië and various shops in the Indische buurt
- 10 minutes by bike to Central Station
- Tram stops for lines 7 and 26 within walking distance

importantInformation.viewings: Contact the real estate agent to schedule a viewing

notes.text: The architecture is amazing. nice location too
